 Real Madrid include Sergio Ramos and Ferland Mendy in the squad to face Chelsea in the return leg of the semi-final of the Champions League at Stamford Bridge. REAL MADRID SQUAD LIST: Goalkeepers: Courtois, Lunin and Altube. Defenders: E. Militão, Sergio Ramos, Nacho, Marcelo, Odriozola, Mendy and Miguel. Midfielders: Kroos, Modrić, Casemiro, Isco, Valverde, Arribas and Blanco. Attackers: Hazard, Benzema, Asensio, Vini Jr., Mariano and Rodrygo. Chelsea played a 1-1 draw in the first leg of the encounter at the Alfredo di Stefano Stadium. Post Views: 
